TextMate assets in this directory are derived from Visual Studio Code
(https://github.com/microsoft/vscode), licensed under the MIT License.

Files:
- json/syntaxes/json.tmLanguage.json  (extensions/json/syntaxes/JSON.tmLanguage.json)
- json/language-configuration.json    (extensions/json/language-configuration.json)
- dark_vs.json                        (extensions/theme-defaults/themes/dark_vs.json)
- light_vs.json                       (extensions/theme-defaults/themes/light_vs.json)

These are loaded at runtime by sora-editor's language-textmate module to provide
JSON syntax highlighting and dark/light color schemes in the config editor.

